cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.GR, cs.MM 

This paper is primarily focused on image synthesis and manipulation, specifically for faces. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision). Additionally, the paper discusses the use of GANs and their latent space, which falls under the category of cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also explores the disentanglement of different facial attributes, which could be categorized under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The manipulation of face pose and fixing of artifacts could fall under cs.GR (Graphics) and cs.MM (Multimedia), respectively.
